                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1" defective="false">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; parts of the Canon Tables, numbers of the “tituli”; elements of the punctuation signs, of the text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
Several groups of lines on the incipit page of Texts I, II, III, IV and V, alternating with black lines; incipit of subsections of Text I; incipit of the chapters and the postscripts of Texts II, III, IV and V.</rubric>
